---
title: Balsamic & Parsley Beef Steak with Sautéed Veggies & Mash
description: There is something so comforting about the aroma of caramelised butter, parsley and vinegar bubbling in a pan.
Completely mouth-watering to say the least. Drizzled over tender steak, atop a mound of creamy potato mash – what’s not
to love?

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
